column4: NSLOCTEXT("[88F937FF4734E01EBCCBBE9D484CF29B]", "BB93D5B14775F2961E03338C2EF48F81", "I will not move for you. You won\'t get past me.")
NSLOCTEXT("[88F937FF4734E01EBCCBBE9D484CF29B]", "51C57A4E4DD29C1CA7AA2DBFD51BC316", "I want to save energy. Fighting him won\'t help me.")
NSLOCTEXT("[88F937FF4734E01EBCCBBE9D484CF29B]", "EE2739674D9C8E6F983AAB914C9B3BFE", "If you beat them maybe I\'ll see you again. Until then, I\'m gone.")
